Beach Eats USA - Season 1, Episode 6




Hidden Gems

Curtis Stone uncovers the beach spots tucked away from the beaten path and serving amazing food to those who know where to find it. There's saffron-infused mussels in Virginia, beef spring rolls filled with ooey, gooey cheese in a California hideaway, and pineapple pork chops grilled to perfection on a tiny island off South Carolina coast.
